                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                sling:resourceType="thallforge/components/core/text"
                text="&lt;h2>What?&lt;/h2>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>ThallForge&amp;nbsp;is a streaming platform dedicated to discovering, streaming, and promoting music. It offers curated music experiences, band recommendations, and access to exclusive content.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;h2>How?&lt;/h2>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>The system user Adobe Experience Manager (AEM) as a main tool for building the website. The author can create pages from all the features that the system contains.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;h2>Why?&lt;/h2>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>The authors need to define all the content that the final users will see on the final streaming platform. The users need a stable and secure background system that will reliable and will provide the data to them.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;h2>When?&lt;/h2>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>The system is available at all times! It was developed in the period between September and October 2024.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                textIsRich="true"/>
